# Trivy ignore file (auto-caricato dalla working dir).
#
# Falso positivo del secret-scanner: @azure/storage-blob include la
# connection-string PUBBLICA e ben nota dell'emulatore Azurite
# (UseDevelopmentStorage=true → account "devstoreaccount1" + AccountKey
# documentata da Microsoft). Finisce nei bundle compilati .next/ e Trivy
# la segnala come "azure-storage-account-key". NON è un segreto reale: i
# segreti di produzione vivono nei Secret Kubernetes, mai nel codice/immagine,
# e sono coperti dal check GitGuardian.
azure-storage-account-key

# CVE-2026-4372 — HuggingFace transformers RCE via untrusted model loading.
# infra/ai/worker pins transformers==4.48.3 as part of a deliberately balanced
# stack (whisperx 3.3.x ← pyannote 3.3 ← numpy 1.x ← torch 2.6.0). The only
# fixed version is 5.3.0, which is incompatible with that stack: dependabot's
# 5.3.0 bump (#116) fails the worker Docker build. The RCE vector requires
# loading an attacker-supplied model/config; the worker only loads pinned,
# trusted HuggingFace models (whisper/pyannote) in an isolated, opt-in batch
# pod with no untrusted-model path. Risk accepted (VEX: not_affected). Revisit
# when whisperx/pyannote support a patched transformers line.
CVE-2026-4372
